      "role": "user",
      "content": "interesting. so u mean like, if someone has naturally very textured/coiled hair, they should probably just straighten it to fit that \"sleek\" look? what about cultural or religious things like hijabs or turbans—do u think those affect how \"authoritative\" someone looks in a boardroom, or should they just stick to more standard western styles to be safe?",
